kafka API:

Core:
Producer API
Consumer API

Extension:
Connector API
Stream API


1. Database/hdfs/external datasource -> Kafka
     |_ Producer API   /  Source Connector

2, Kafka -> Database/hdfs/external datasource
     |_ Consumer API   / Sink Connector

3. Kafka -> Kafka
    |_ Consumer API & Producer API  / Stream API

4. App -> Kafka
    |_ Producer API

5. Kafka -> App
    |_ Consumer API




